summary: This code imports the 'solargraph' library, initializes a new instance of Solargraph::ApiMap, retrieves all methods associated with the 'String' class, and then prints those method names.

details.comment: This code imports the 'solargraph' library, initializes a new instance of Solargraph::ApiMap, retrieves all methods associated with the 'String' class, and then prints those method names.
details.content:
require 'solargraph'
api_map = Solargraph::ApiMap.new
pins = api_map.get_methods('String')
print(pins)
